data.description: They'll Gather Here! Friends & Family will love being able to all fit around the dining table or sit next to the fireplace without being squeezed in. There's plenty of bedroom space for the grand-kids & their parents. A great place for a home business or hobby of any type. Imagine the gals soaking up the sun around the pool and the guys having fun on their ATV roaming the 10 ACRES! Don't just think about it CALL TODAY!
